Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli wannan shaida mai ban sha'awa a tashoshin talabijin guda shida na ranar Alhamis, daga mai neman zama a babban kotun tarayya, Bret Kavanaugh, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da samun matsala a siyasa, yayin da tashoshin talabijin suka katse shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum saboda juyin juya halin da aka yi a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi, ta ce, FBI za ta gudanar da binciken da ake yi na mako guda.
