Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin shaidar da ya yi da-na-sani, ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
A ranar Jumma'a, an yi rahoton cewa mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan wa'azi.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin kallon tashoshin talabijin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
