Da bugun da Menga ya yi, Livingston ta ci Rangers da ci 1-0
Dolly Menga ta ci kwallo ta farko a Livingston ta tabbatar da nasara
Livingston ya yi wa Rangers biris, kuma Steven Gerrard ya yi rashin nasara a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin Ibrox.
Harbin Dolly Mengo ya kawo canji, kuma tawagar Gary Holt ta yi daidai da tawagar Hibernian a matsayi na biyu.
A sakamakon haka, Gerrard ya ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin gasar cin kofin duniya a bana, kuma a ranar Lahadi mai zuwa, Hearts za su ci gaba da zama a kan gaba, inda za su kasance maki takwas a baya.
Kafin a fara, Rangers za su yi wasa da Rapid Vienna a gasar Europa League a ranar Alhamis.
A halin yanzu Livingston ya kara rashin cin kwallaye a gasar zuwa wasanni shida, kuma kocin Holt, wanda ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan da ya gabata, bai taba shan kashi ba.
Livingston ya ɓata damar da kai tsaye a kan baƙo
Ya kamata tawagar Holt ta kasance a kan gaba tun kafin a yi harin, domin sun jawo wa Rangers matsala da yawa ta hanyar kai tsaye.
Scott Robinson ya yi nasara, amma ya jefa ƙwallo a cikin ƙofar, sannan Alan Lithgow ya buga ƙofar, Craig Halkett ya buga ƙwallo.
Masu masaukin sun bar Rangers su yi wasa domin sun san cewa za su iya zama barazana ga masu masaukin a lokacin da aka katse wasannin.
Kuma ta haka ne suka kai ga maƙasudin.
Rangers sun ba Livingston kyauta, kuma Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun shirya wani aiki don Menga, wanda ya yi harbi kuma ya buga daga tsakiyar filin wasa.
Rangers sun fi samun kwallon, amma ba su iya tsallake 'yan wasan gida ba, kuma mai tsaron gidan Liam Kelly bai da aiki sosai.
Wannan tsari ya ci gaba a rabi na biyu, duk da cewa Alfredo Morelos ya yi amfani da kariya ga Kelly.
Mai tsaron ragar Rangers Allan McGregor ya kare da kafa daga harbin da Scott Pittman ya yi, yayin da Lithgow ya yi birgima daga wani bugun da Livingston ya yi a harin.
An ci gaba da gabatar da karar a wurin shari'ar Livingston, amma 'yan gidan sun yi watsi da duk wani harin, tare da laifuffuka biyu  Halkett ya yi laifi a kan maye gurbin Glenn Middleton da kuma laifin wasan hannu  kuma mai hukunci bai yanke hukunci ba.
