An yi wa luwadi yancin kisa a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna wa mutanen LGBT wariya sosai.
Saboda ra'ayoyin da suka dace da al'adun gargajiya, an gano cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90% na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mace.
