"Tattaunawar wasu kasashe na uku a cikin samar da makamashi na da matukar damuwa a gare ni", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
