Sauran muhimman halaye sun hada da tsawon lokaci tsakanin kulawa  sabon jirgin ruwa zai iya zama a waje da tashar tashar jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Jaridar Die Ziet ta lura cewa, jinkiri da ake samu yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa masu ƙarfi da aka ce za su ba wa Jamus damar yin tasiri a ƙasashen waje, za su zama marasa amfani a lokacin da aka soma amfani da su.
Frigate F125 da ta yi hatsari ta zama sananniyar sanarwa a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ƙi karɓar jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi ga kamfanin Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne lokaci na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgin zuwa ginin bayan sun kawo shi.
An san kadan game da dalilan dawowar, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun nuna wasu mahimman ƙwarewar software da fasaha waɗanda zasu sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi zuwa aikin yaƙi.
Rashin ingancin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci musamman saboda jiragen Baden-Wuerttemberg zasuyi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa kimanin 120  kawai rabin ma'aikatan tsoffin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke rage ƙarfinsa kuma yana iyakance damar da sojojin ruwa ke da shi don haɓaka ta nan gaba.
Jirgin ruwan mai nauyin tan 7000 mai suna Rhineland-Palatinate ya ninka na jiragen ruwa masu kama da irin na Jamus a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga rashin kayan aiki, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya  gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin ya zama matsala.
Wannan ya kamata ya kai €3.1 biliyan (US$3.6 biliyan)  daga €2.2 biliyan na farko.
Matsalar sabbin jirage masu saukar ungulu na zama na musamman a cikin hasken gargaɗin kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokoki ta Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwan sun "ragu da jiragen ruwa da za su iya turawa".
Wani jami'in ya ce batun ya tsananta da shigewar lokaci, saboda an rushe tsoffin jiragen ruwa kuma ba a samar da wasu jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi nadamar cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na ajin Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga rundunar.
