Wani jami'i daga jami'ar jihar Tennessee ya gaya wa Chris Harris a tashar WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee, cewa Abercrombie yana murmurewa bayan tiyata a Cibiyar Kiwon Lafiya ta Vanderbilt.
