A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai ƙaru.
A lokacin da aka katse hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an agaji da ke yankin Donggala, yankin da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5, ba su samu wani bayani ba.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu bayan girgizar kasa.
Wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggali a Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin Central Sulawesi, lardin da ke kan iyakar bakin tekun da ke yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda a shekarar 2017 aka kiyasta yawansa ya kai 379,800.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami suka addabi birnin, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40.
Donggala yanki ne da ya kai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar tekun da ke arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, an kiyasta cewa Regency, wani yanki na yanki, yana da yawan mutane 299,000.
Babban ayyukan tattalin arziki na lardin Central Sulawesi sune kiwon kifi da noma, musamman a yankin Donggala na tsakiya.
Har ila yau, ana samun muhimmiyar aiki a yankin na ma'adinan nickel, wanda galibi ke faruwa a Morovali, a gefen Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Indonesiya ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami sun yi wa Palu da Donggala illa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya addabi yankin Donggala na arewacin kasar, kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
Domin Indonesia tana zaune a kan wani yanki mai cike da girgizar ƙasa da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire, ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
A shekarun baya bayan nan, an yi wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami kamar haka:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na arewacin Sumatra a Indonesia a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya addabi kasashe 14 inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani irin girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin Indonesia da ke da yawan jama'a, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya mamaye gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afka kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gundumar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da mutuwa da kuma fargaba yayin da mutane ke tunawa da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Wannan lokacin ba tsunami ba ne, amma gine-gine da suka rushe sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon bude ido zuwa wurin.
