Labarin Red Tide: Ruwa Mai Yawa Ya Rage A Yankin Yankin Pinellas, Manatee, da Saratosa
Wani rahoto na kwanan nan da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida (FWC) ta fitar ya nuna cewa, a wasu wurare a yankin Tampa Bay, an sami raguwar yawan ruwan sama.
Hukumar FWC ta ba da rahoton ƙarin fure a wurare na Pinellas, Manatee, Saratosa, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Ruwa mai ruwan sama ya kai mil 130 daga gabar arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudancin Lee County.
Za a iya ganin wannan hasken a wajen mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa ba kamar yadda aka gani ba a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu ruwa mai jan ruwa a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaitan taro a Pinellas County da kewayen tekun, low zuwa high a kan gabar tekun Hillsborough County, low zuwa high a Manatee County, low zuwa high a kan gabar tekun Saratoza County da kewayen tekun, low zuwa matsakaici a kan gabar tekun Charlotte County, low zuwa high a kan gabar tekun Lee County da kewayen tekun, da kuma low a kan gabar tekun Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni na tashin hankali a cikin numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier.
Babu wani rahoton da ya nuna cewa akwai wani ciwo a numfashi a yankin arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
